VERSION HISTORY
===========================================================================
Version 1.1.000
o  Merged configuration files
o  Added config.help
o  Improved email notification

Version 1.0.002
o  Fixed bug caused by RecursiveDirectoryIterator, which re-processes a
   file if its base name is changed while iterating

Version 1.0.001
o  Fixed bug where files could be doubly processed
o  The harvester, master publisher and www publisher can now be run at
   will and whenever without running the risk of corrupting the file
   system, the backup server and/or the media database
o  Added this README file

